snippet.title: We Are Chicago - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
We Are Chicago will be released on February 9th, 2017!

For more information and to pre-order the game check out our website or find us on Twitter!

http://wearechicagogame.com/
http://twitter.com/WeRChicagoGame

Music by George Hufnagl
http://www.soundslikegeorge.com/
